   * @param success - Callback functin which will be called in a sucessful payment
   * @param failure - Callback functin which will be called upon failure
   * 
   * Amount Examples: 1000 - $10.00, 612400 - $6,124.00
   * 
   * Accepted types Examples: ['VISA', 'MASTERCARD', 'IOU', 'BITCOIN']
   * All possible values for accepted_types:
   * AMERICANEXPRESS, BITCOIN, DINERSCLUBCARD, IOWEYOU, MASTERCARD, VISA
   * 
   * Success Callback - function (reciept) { ... }
   * 
   * Failure Callback - funciton (error) { ... }
   * 
